&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333;&#34;&gt;&amp;#x5177;&amp;#x4F53;&amp;#x53EF;&amp;#x4EE5;&amp;#x67E5;&amp;#x770B;gtags&amp;#x548C;global&amp;#x7684;man page&amp;#x3002;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; font-weight: 700; font-size: 27px; color: #333;&#34;&gt;SpaceVim&amp;#x7684;gtags layer&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333;&#34;&gt;&amp;#x5148;&amp;#x770B;&amp;#x4E00;&amp;#x4E0B;gtags layer&amp;#x7684;&amp;#x5FEB;&amp;#x6377;&amp;#x952E;&amp;#xFF1A;&lt;br&gt;

        &lt;img class=&#34;enMedia&#34; src=&#34;/images/SpaceVim gtags and cscope/1566114231052&#34; hash=&#34;4ac7cf2da331fdb47bdaa748ad702d06&#34; align alt longdesc width=&#34;1352&#34; height=&#34;478&#34; border hspace vspace usemap style title lang xml:lang dir&gt;
      &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ddd; padding: 0 15px; color: #777;&#34;&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333; margin-top: 0;&#34;&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; font-weight: 700;&#34;&gt;:GtagsGenerate[!] {bang}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Update gtags for current file, with a {bang}, will update the project&amp;apos;s gtags database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333;&#34;&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; font-weight: 700;&#34;&gt;:Gtags -r func&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
To go to the referenced point of func, add -r option.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333;&#34;&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; font-weight: 700;&#34;&gt;:Gtags -f main.c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
To get list of objects in a file &amp;apos;main.c&amp;apos;, use -f command.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; margin: 10px 0; color: #333; margin-bottom: 0;&#34;&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34;line-height: 160%; box-sizing: content-box; font-weight: 700;&#34;&gt;:Gtags -f %&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
If you are editing `main.c&amp;apos; itself, you can use &amp;apos;%&amp;apos; instead.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
